title: Catwoman 21 (Tablet Edition)
description:
This is from the original scanner. I adjusted the resolution and compressed the file for easier reading on tablets and ereaders. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.


Catwoman 21

By:   	Ann Nocenti, Rafael Sandoval, Terry Dodson	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Superhero
Series:   	Catwoman
Publisher:   	DC Comics	
Pub. Date:  	June 26, 2013
Format:         CBZ

Following the events of the CATWOMAN ANNUAL, Catwoman and the Penguin declare war on each other -- and Gotham City is set to burn in their wake!
